requirement for DRS/vMotion 
vmkernal is configured to both the Hosts.
storage should be common.
permissions should be ok.

DRS/Vmotion start process:

1. check the resource to other machine host like cpu ram etc.
2. create snapshot in source destination while vmdisk is created to destination Host.
3. cpu ram i/o output continously moved to destination Host.
4. once all the resources moved to destination location. 
5. snapshot removed from source Host and power up VMs to the destination Host.
